From bf9b3f26336c0ddce330e1c392373d17b548ef4c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Yuvasree Sivasankaran <ysivasan@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Wed, 9 Jul 2025 16:12:07 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:DP:wifi:ath12k: Support for stats interface and
 aggregation

Add interface and aggregate support for peer, vif and pdev stats
at both MLD and link level like below

Link peer - Peer stats of that link peer
MLD peer - aggregation of all link peer stats
Link vif - Vif stats of that vif and aggregation of
all link peers in that vif
MLD vif - Aggregation of all link vif in that MLD vif
and also aggregation of all link peer in each link vif
Pdev - Aggregation of  all link vif's in that pdev and their
respective link peers

These interface and aggregate api's are used by the handlers
of NL vendor subcmds to get the respective stats.

Patch Dependency:
        0425-0002-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-DP-Telemetry-in-Tx-Enqueue.patch
        0426-0005-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Telemetry-counters-in-Tx-com.patch
        0427-0001-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Add-Telemetry-counter-in-Rx-.patch
        0428-0001-UPSTREAM-DP-Add-support-for-Rx-WBM-Error-stats.patch

Signed-off-by: Yuvasree Sivasankaran <ysivasan@qti.qualcomm.com>
